{"tid":1647033,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 民陣10.20可唔可以搞返次「九龍」版本百萬大遊行啊？","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T05:03:21.000Z","uid":167548,"like":111,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1cf8730deb2a6f90cc000d1bcc7e977e134e80","tid":1647033,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"推到民陣申請遊行！<br />\n預計下面留言會屌鳩我送頭撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是我提出今次遊行由<br />\n九龍塘香港城市大學為起點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路經理大直落尖沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是如果民陣吹雞號召力至少有幾十萬香港人總動員沒懼反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行路線可以交由民陣思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今鋪曬佢爛話比全世界聽香港人每隔兩個月就可以推返次百萬行出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n屌你老母樓主水鳩手足去送頭唔去遊行啦，合法遊行沒耐就射TG㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n樓主諗住搏班癲狗唔會是Shitty起點射TG, <br />\n如果唔是直送世界頭版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n利申我信會射入Shitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實當初10.1實彈射中手足, 民陣已經出聲想搞聲援健仔大遊行, 但是我見日程表沒位比佢放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, <br />\n反對通知書是宣傳遊行最好嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個星期日遍地開花,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下個星期日百萬遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9dbf4a4af83435e992cbd568a53e830d9ca5bb","tid":1647033,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"推 留定下星期日全家出嚟遊行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d379c99b8b767c29451df2b8377e2791105f43","tid":1647033,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"今次唔撚再去港島啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ce4d0fb772bfa531981e806c2498ba09200465","tid":1647033,"uid":173552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cedcd0dade8ad0fe5805ebc16cd4af938178d82","tid":1647033,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"民陣係咪訓著左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突發！香城online現已公開發售！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9644c7be52fd39089df684b4ebc9e60d1c5d296","tid":1647033,"uid":97736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a56e573b94856acaabfdff2324059eedcdcaa65e","tid":1647033,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"民陣時候出手啦 <br />\n你地班泛民黎生日日曬蘋果出風向文 <br />\n今鋪比10.20靚日你地去搞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991ec956e53599ea91437bee15ae9d6ebb6bb02a","tid":1647033,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"去九龍驚閪你黨鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a735147b8e4e27717065306f2ddd96d4d447dd","tid":1647033,"uid":309137,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"想要百萬級<br 